contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionarypar|garda|Garda}} '''Garda''' may refer to: * ''An [[Garda Síochána]]'', the national police of the Republic of Ireland * [[Garda National Surveillance Unit]], the domestic intelligence agency of the Republic of Ireland. * [[Lake Garda]], a lake in northern Italy. * [[Garda (VR)]], a commune on the shores of the Italian Lake Garda in the province of Verona. * Garda, Sweden, a town on Gotland Island, Sweden. * ''[[Garda Financiară]]'', the Romanian control and tax law-enforcement agency. * The [[Garda hitch]], a knot used in rock climbing and rescue. * [[Garda (security company)]], a security and protection company headquartered in Montreal, Quebec, Canada. {{disambig}}
